{"word":"ἡδύπνοος","slug":"ἡδύπνοος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἡδύπνοος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πνέω'><el>πνέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>sweet-breathing</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; of musical sound, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>; of dreams, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>sweet-smelling, fragrant</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}